data.description:
Take a look at this charming, newly painted 3 bed 2 bath brick home situated on a beautiful 1.51 acres. 
Here you can have the best of both worlds with country living and easy access to the Kickapoo Turnpike. 
This home is all electric, it has a new hot water tank as well as a water softener, and new carpet. The covered back patio is a nice relaxing retreat to settle in after a long day.
